window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The end is coming. The only way out is to go all in.</b></p> <p>Picking up the pieces after another devastating betrayal, Gunnar aims to change the cutthroat city of Thailen for good. If that means outsmarting a powerful sorceress and starting a guild war, then so be it.</p> <p>Meanwhile, Em holds a secret to Gunnar's past that could alter everything he thought he knew about Pantheon Online. Soon, Gunnar must reckon between the truth and his reality in this new world. His decision will change everything.</p> <p>Don't miss the wild, battle-crazed conclusion to the Pantheon Online trilogy!</p>"; 
